Class BaseModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • in.co.sunrays.ocha.model.BaseModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DropdownListBean, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<BaseModel>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AttendenceModel, BranchModel, CollegeModel, CommentModel, DepartementModel, EResourceModel, NoticeModel, RoleModel, StaffModel, StudentModel, SubjectModel, TimeTableModel, UserModel

    public abstract class BaseModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, DropdownListBean, java.lang.Comparable<BaseModel>
    Base Model containing common attributes and methods. It implements Comparable interface that compares two objects on the basis of primary key ID. It implements DropdownListBean interface, that is used to make HTML Drop List from Model collection.
